.container-fluid
 .row-fluid
  ul.breadcrumb
    li.active
      a(href="#/") Home
  .span3
    .well
      .small-btn.btn.right
        i.icon-trash
          |  Clear History
      ul.nav.nav-list
        li
          small Most recently browsed builds
        li(ng-repeat='b in recent.recent_builds')
           a(href='{{b.link}}') {{b.caption}}
        li.divider
        li
          small Most recently browsed builders
        li(ng-repeat='b in recent.recent_builders')
           a(href='{{b.link}}') {{b.caption}}
  .span8
    .well
      h2 Welcome to buildbot
      | Probably we should display information about the current config
      .row-fluid
        .span4
          ul
            li Buildbot version: {{config.bbversion}}
            li Twisted version: {{config.txversion}}
        .span4
          ul
            li Project Name: {{config.projectname}}
            li Project Version: {{config.projectversion}}
            li Project Url: {{config.projecturl}}
        small.span4

          | buildbot-www is using the following open-source JavaScript libraries:
          ul
            li(ng-repeat='module in config.bower_configs')
              a(href='{{module.http_url}}') {{module.name}}
              | : {{module.version}}
